Alright Rebecca, now I see that after graduating from university your first job was...
好的，Rebecca，现在我注意到你大学毕业后第一份工作是……

111
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:30,920
For a local paper in York called the York Herald.
在约克一家本地报纸，叫《约克先驱报》。

112
