Actually I started with them as an intern.
实际上，我是以实习生身份开始的。

113
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:37,320
I was really keen on getting some experience in journalism and this seemed like a good
我当时非常渴望获得一些新闻工作经验，这看起来是一个不错的

114
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:38,880
first step.
第一步。

115
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,920
Certainly.
当然。

116
